  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350\u00b0F (175\u00b0C).",
    "Slice the gluten\u2011free bread and toast in the oven until lightly golden, about 5 minutes.",
    "In a medium bowl, combine diced cucumber, halved cherry tomatoes, diced red onion, diced avocado, and chopped cilantro.",
    "In a separate small bowl, whisk the lime juice, olive oil, salt, pepper, and cream of tartar until the mixture emulsifies.",
    "Drizzle the dressing over the vegetables and toss gently to combine.",
    "Arrange the toasted bread slices on a serving plate and spoon the dressed salad over each slice.",
    "Sprinkle roasted sesame seeds and optional chili flakes on top.",
    "Serve immediately for the best crispness."
